## 4. Exact Component Inventory & Styling Tokens

This is the block-level inventory to build.
*   **`GlobalNavbar`**: Sticky. `backdrop-blur-md`. Transparent bg becomes `rgba(10,10,10, 0.8)` on scroll. Border bottom: `1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05)`.
*   **`GlobalTheme`**: Background: `bg-[#0A0A0A]`. Text: `text-white`. Secondary Text: `text-zinc-400`.
*   **`HeroH1Text`**: Fluid typography using CSS `clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem)`. `letter-spacing: -0.04em`. Font: `font-sans` (Inter/Geist). Weight: `font-extrabold`.
*   **`ButtonPrimary`**: Solid Emerald (`bg-[#10B981]`). Hover state: `transform: translateY(-1px)` + `box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3)`. Border radius: `6px`. Text: `"Book Demo"`, never `"Book Demo 🚀"`.
*   **`ButtonGhost`**: Transparent. Box border: `1px solid rgba(255,255,255, 0.1)`. Hover state: `background: rgba(255,255,255, 0.05)`.
*   **`BentoCard`**: The core structural unit. Background: `rgba(255,255,255,0.02)`. Border: `1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)`. Border-Radius: `12px`. Hover: Border color transitions to `rgba(255,255,255, 0.2)`. Transition: `border 300ms ease`.
*   **`LogosMarquee`**: Infinite CSS animation (translateX). Will-change: transform.
*   **`FloatingUIAsset`**: A wrapper for hero/bento images that applies a subtle `translateY` floating looping animation. `animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite`.

---

## 5. Exact Motion Tokens

No linear animations. We use specific cubic-beziers.
*   **Easing Token (Standard Vercel/Linear Snappy):** `cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)` -> Use for Modals opening, Accordion expansion, Bento card hover states.
*   **Easing Token (Soft/Float):** `cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.25, 1)` -> Use for Continuous hero asset floating, tooltip fades.
*   **Duration - Micro (Hover/State change):** `150ms`.
*   **Duration - Macro (Section Reveals/Layout Shifts):** `600ms`.

**Implementation of Section Reveals:**
Elements entering the viewport start with `opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px) scale(0.98);` and transition to `opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1);` over 600ms `cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)`.

